
  <sn><md>#### Importance of studying geography and environment:

```
          Geography &amp; Environment
                     │
   ┌─────────────────┼─────────────────┐
   │                 │                 │
 Nature          Society          Resources
   │                 │                 │
 Landforms      Communication      Ocean
 Climate        Disaster           Economy
 Plants         Agriculture        Management
   │                 │                 │
   └─────────────────┴─────────────────┘
                     │
               Knowledge
```

* Through reading Geography and Environment chapter, we can know
* The nature and environment of a particular place of the earth.
* Cause of formation and features of mountains, hills, rivers, oceans, plateaus, plains and deserts.
* Acquisition of scientific conceptions about the evolution of the animal world since the birth of the earth.
* About plants and animals and their variety in conducts, food habits and lifestyles.
* Changes made in social environment due to the development in agriculture, industry, trade and commerce, transportation and communication
* About cause of natural disaster casualties and control, geographical position, pattern of climate and importance of communication system.
* Increase of temperature of the earth, greenhouse effect and its influence.
* Gaining economic solvency by man using natural resources.
* Ocean and ocean resource management.
</md></sn>
